.SH NAME
snd_soc_set_runtime_hwparams \- set the runtime hardware parameters
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" snd_soc_set_runtime_hwparams
.BI "(struct snd_pcm_substream *substream "  ","
.BI "const struct snd_pcm_hardware *hw "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "substream" 12
the pcm substream
.IP "hw" 12
the hardware parameters
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
